msgid "Exporters"
msgstr "出口商"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Default"
msgstr "默认"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Quarkus OpenTelemetry extension uses its own signal exporters built on top of Vert.x for optimal performance and maintainability. All *Quarkus built in exporters use the OTLP protocol* through a couple of data senders, using `grpc` (the default) and `http/protobuf`."
msgstr "为了优化性能和可维护性，Quarkus OpenTelemetry 扩展使用了自己构建在 Vert.x 基础上的信号输出程序。所有 *Quarkus 内置的输出程序* 都通过几个数据发送器 *使用 OTLP 协议* ，使用 `grpc` （默认）和 `http/protobuf` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The active exporter is automatically wired by CDI, that's why the `quarkus.otel.traces.exporter`, `quarkus.otel.metrics.exporter` and `quarkus.otel.logs.exporter` properties default value is `cdi`. This is not because of the protocol being used in the data transfer but because of how the exporters are wired."
msgstr "活动的输出程序由 CDI 自动布线，这就是为什么 `quarkus.otel.traces.exporter` 、 `quarkus.otel.metrics.exporter` 和 `quarkus.otel.logs.exporter` 属性的默认值是 `cdi` 的原因。这不是因为数据传输中使用的协议，而是因为出口程序的连接方式。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "CDI (Context Dependency Injection) will manage the exporters to use, according to the selected protocol or when applications implement their own CDI exporter, like in tests."
msgstr "CDI（上下文依赖注入）将根据所选协议或应用程序实现自己的 CDI 输出程序（如在测试中）来管理要使用的输出程序。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `quarkus.otel.exporter.otlp.protocol` property instructs Quarkus to switch the senders and defaults to `grpc` but `http/protobuf` can also be used."
msgstr "`quarkus.otel.exporter.otlp.protocol` 属性指示 Quarkus 切换发送器，默认为 `grpc` ，但也可以使用 `http/protobuf` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you change the protocol, you also need to change the port in the endpoint. The default port for `grpc` is `4317` and for `http/protobuf` is `4318`."
msgstr "如果更改协议，还需要更改端点的端口。 `grpc` 的默认端口是 `4317` ， `http/protobuf` 的默认端口是 `4318` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `quarkus.otel.exporter.otlp.memory-mode` property configures the memory allocation strategy for OTLP exporters.\n"
"The default value `immutable-data` creates new serialization objects for each export.\n"
"Setting it to `reusable-data` enables object pooling to reduce garbage collection pressure, which can be beneficial in memory-constrained environments."
msgstr "`quarkus.otel.exporter.otlp.memory-mode` 属性用于配置 OTLP 输出程序的内存分配策略。默认值 `immutable-data` 会为每次导出创建新的序列化对象。将其设置为 `可重用数据（reusable-data）` 可启用对象池以减少垃圾收集压力，这在内存受限的环境中很有益处。"

